comments: Caruso (CHI) makes contact to Barrett's (NYK) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Robinson (NYK) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) shot attempt at the basket and avoids making contact.
Caruso (CHI) moves into Barrett's (NYK) path and initiates contact to his body and arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) makes contact to DeRozan's (CHI) arm that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) legally contests Barrett's (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) firms up in a screening position in Burks' (NYK) path and does not deliver contact.
Burks (NYK) legally contests DeRozan's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Vucevic (CHI) makes incidental contact with Robinson (NYK) that does not affect his ability to control the rebound.
Randle (NYK) and DeRozan (CHI) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
LaVine (CHI) legally contests Burks' (NYK) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
DeRozan (CHI) dislodges Burks (NYK) from his defensive position at the end of his drive to the basket.
White (CHI) initiates body contact with Randle (NYK) that affects his SQBR.
Robinson (NYK) makes contact to LaVine's (CHI) arm that affects his shot attempt at the rim.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
